4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed for aspiring tech professionals. In this 18-week program, students will master key technologies such as JavaScript and Python, which are in high demand in the job market. Over the course, participants will engage in coding, algorithm scripting, and app development, culminating in a personal project to showcase their skills. 

Classes consist of three sessions per week, maintaining a low teacher-to-student ratio for personalized learning. No prior coding experience is necessary, and courses can be taken in either English or Spanish. Graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate.

